title: Kehlani at #BeatsxRootsJam | Make It Rain
description:
After Kehlani slayed the stage, she joined us in the Backroom to play "Make it Rain." You never know what's going to happen at the Beats x Roots Jam Session.

Beats by Dre

transcripts: What’s up it’s Kehlani here in the backroom at the Roots Jam. We’re about to see who’s going to kick each others butt in this dang game, lets go! Where would you start? Wait wait wait wait, on your mark, get set, go! Ahh no haha, I think I’m kicking your butt, uh look no fair, I totally like was hitting it with the double action and he just took the whole thing out and threw it like it was cool, like . Oh okay, make it rain in Kleenex, this is what they’re dancing for these days, handing out napkins like it’s nothing haha. I’ll see you at the championships bro, good game.
